  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 9-7-15, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REVISE THE JUDICIAL PRECINCTS FOR THE FOURTH CIRCUIT COURT DISTRICT; TO BRING FORWARD SECTION 9-7-17, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, WHICH PROVIDES THE NUMBER OF JUDGES FOR THE FOURTH CIRCUIT COURT DISTRICT; TO AMEND SECTION 9-7-23, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REVISE THE PRECINCTS FOR THE SEVENTH CIRCUIT COURT DISTRICT FOR THE \"FROM JANUARY 1, 2027, UNTIL JANUARY 1, 2031\" TIER FOR THE SEVENTH CIRCUIT COURT DISTRICT; TO BRING FORWARD SECTION 9-7-25, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, WHICH PROVIDES THE NUMBER OF JUDGES FOR THE SEVENTH CIRCUIT COURT DISTRICT; TO PROVIDE CONDITIONAL QUALIFYING DEADLINES FOR JUDICIAL CANDIDATES FOR THE 4TH AND 7TH CIRCUIT COURT DISTRICTS; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
